Date of Birth: 18 July 1961<br/>
Birthplace: Carlisle, Cumberland, England<br/>
Ordained as an apostle: 7 December 2023<br/>
<br/>
He married Jennifer Carole Hulme in January 1991. They are the parents of four children.
After joining the Church on Christmas Eve in 1987, Patrick Kearon served in numerous Church callings, including ward Young Men president, counselor in a bishopric, branch president, stake president, and Area Seventy.
Elder Kearon served as a member of the Presidency of the Seventy from 2017 to 2023. He was named senior president of the Seventy in August 2020.
